  "title": "Customer Service cum Logistics Coordinator (1 year contract) | 5Day, West, MNC [R22107578]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Basic salary up to $3500</p></li><li><p>Mon to Fri, 9am to 6pm</p></li><li><p>1 year contract (Renewable/ Extendable)</p></li><li><p>Friendly and collaborative work environment</p></li><li><p>On job training provided</p></li><li><p>Location: Clementi</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle customer enquiries and service requests, ensuring timely resolution and customer satisfaction</p></li><li><p>Coordinate service planning and track service orders to ensure on-time instrument servicing</p></li><li><p>Work closely with internal teams and logistics partners to manage repairs, materials, and shipments</p></li><li><p>Manage outsourced and overseas repair processes, including documentation and follow-up</p></li><li><p>Monitor service turnaround time (TAT) and operational performance</p></li><li><p>Prepare service reports and support continuous process improvements</p></li><li><p>Assist with other operational and business support tasks as required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min Higher Nitec/ Diploma in Supply Chain/ Managmeent or equivalent.</p></li><li><p>Experience in administration/ customer service/ operations planning is preferred.</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Office; ERP system experience is a plus</p></li><li><p>Entry-level candidates are welcome, on job training will be provided.</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>To Apply, kindly click on the \"APPLY NOW\" button.</strong></p><p><strong>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Jasmine Wong (R22107578)</strong></p>",
